fields.description: The display name of the app that is the source of the mobile app relationship entity. For example: Orca. Maximum length is 500 characters. Read-Only. Supports: $select. Does not support $search, $filter, $orderBy. This property is read-only.
fields.name: SourceDisplayName

fields.description: The display version of the app that is the source of the mobile app relationship entity. For example 1.0.12 or 1.2203.156 or 3. Read-Only. Supports: $select. Does not support $search, $filter, $orderBy. This property is read-only.
fields.name: SourceDisplayVersion

fields.description: The unique app identifier of the source of the mobile app relationship entity. For example: 2dbc75b9-e993-4e4d-a071-91ac5a218672. If null during relationship creation, then it will be populated with parent Id. Read-Only. Supports: $select. Does not support $search, $filter, $orderBy. This property is read-only.
fields.name: SourceId

fields.description: The publisher display name of the app that is the source of the mobile app relationship entity. For example: Fabrikam. Maximum length is 500 characters. Read-Only. Supports: $select. Does not support $search, $filter, $orderBy. This property is read-only.
fields.name: SourcePublisherDisplayName

fields.description: The display name of the app that is the target of the mobile app relationship entity. For example: Firefox Setup 52.0.2 32bit.intunewin. Maximum length is 500 characters.
